- Great work, guys.

1258
00:57:00,943 --> 00:57:02,077
Thanks, Dong-yeon.

1259
00:57:02,144 --> 00:57:03,545
Enjoy your food.

1260
00:57:04,179 --> 00:57:05,447
Thanks for the tofu with kimchi.

1261
00:57:09,318 --> 00:57:11,887
HAPPY

1262
00:57:12,121 --> 00:57:13,122
It's really good.

1263
00:57:13,188 --> 00:57:14,924
