You guys really cleaned it up.
I thought there'd be leftovers.

1302
00:59:14,343 --> 00:59:17,413
THEY FINISH THEIR FIRST MEAL
BEFORE THEY GET CUSTOMERS

1303
00:59:20,015 --> 00:59:21,383
That was a good meal.

1304
